  section.about
    h1 About Downtown Donuts

    p Downtown Donuts has been family-owned since 1992, serving fresh donuts and coffee to the downtown community every morning.

    p What started as a small neighborhood donut shop has grown into a local favorite for handcrafted donuts, warm coffee, and friendly service.

    p We believe a good day can start with something simple: a fresh glazed donut, a hot cup of coffee, and a place that feels welcoming.

    p Every batch is made with care, and every customer is part of our story.

